The following query is not working anymore with ES 5.0 : see [here](https://discuss.elastic.co/t/wildcard-query-over--all-field-on-elasticsearch-5-failed/67315/2)

```
GET g_contents/_search
{
  "query": {
              "wildcard" : {
                "_all" : {
                  "wildcard" : "*doc*",
                  "boost": 1
                }
              }
            }
      }
```

Instead we got the error: 
```

{
