	"filter": [{
		"range": {
			"opening_date_long": {
				"gte": 1481624898000
			}
		}
	}]
}
```

this works fine.

for me it seems that the date range filter is breaking the function_score "boost_mode": "sum" and forcing the child score to get **multiplied** by its parent opposed to a custom mode, "sum", "avg", etc...

